qemacs: qemacs (Quick Emacs text editor)
qemacs:
qemacs: QEmacs is a small but powerful UNIX editor targeted at embedded
qemacs: systems or debugging. Although it is very small, it has some
qemacs: features that even big editors lack. It features multi-window
qemacs: editing, full Unicode/UTF-8 support, shell mode with full color
qemacs: VT100 terminal emulation, binary/hexadecimal editing, and automatic
qemacs: syntax coloring for C mode. It can also open huge files using
qemacs: memory mapping without delay.
